<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>*Shakes Head*</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Gray Rage (DB)">Gray Rage (DB)</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 8:36 p.m. 28/4/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> *Shakes Head*<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=1971" TARGET=_self>PvP Server not All its Cut out To Be</A> (Keira {BC})
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>> Well, I can say this with certainty. If you are a nice person

<BR>&gt; who wants to play EQ to enjoy the game and do a little
<BR>&gt; adventuring then Rallos Zek is not for you. In fact, if you are
<BR>&gt; the kind of person that enjoys playing the game and wants to
<BR>&gt; have fun adventuring around Norrath then dont play on Zek. In
<BR>&gt; that case, Rallos Zek is the worst server you can play on.
<P>IT IS SURELY NOT A PLACE FOR ONE OF SQUEAMISH HEART.
<P>&gt; Here me out, I have played many online fantasy role playing
<BR>&gt; games before and I always found them to be fun (with an
<BR>&gt; exception to UO). In those games I usually played a healer of
<BR>&gt; some kind. Healers are put on this world to help people. Being
<BR>&gt; the nice person that I am, I have always chose to take on a
<BR>&gt; healing profession. This involves self sacrifice. Well! One
<BR>&gt; thing I learned on the PvP srever is that there is no such thing
<BR>&gt; as self sacrifice. Rallos Zek is a free for all, do whatever you
<BR>&gt; want, anarchy. Here is an example:
<P>NO IT'S NOT. RACIAL MURDER IS A RARETY BECAUSE NO PURE PKER CAN LIVE LONG IN THIS GAME WITH NO FRIENDS. THE CUMMINCATIONS IN THE GAME ARE JUST TO GOOD TO LET THEM GET AWAY WITH IT FOR LONG. MAKE TO MANY ENEMIES AND YOU WILL FIND LEVELING VERY HARD AS PEOPLE JUMP YOU ALL THE TIME.
<P>&gt; The other day I was Afk for a matter of minutes outside of
<BR>&gt; Befallen and of course was immediately attacked.
<P>DOH!!!! ARE U NUTS MAN? IF YOU ARE GONNA GO AWAY FROM KEYBOARD YOU MIGHT WANT TO FIND A SAFER PLACE THAN THE FRONT OF BEFALLEN. JUST THINK OF OUR SERVER AS HAVING ALOT LESSS SAFE SPOTS TO GO AFK. THAT SURELY IS NOT A SAFE SPOT.
<P>You see, when
<BR>&gt; these scumbags realized we were afk and not fighting back, they
<BR>&gt; decided to attack.
<P>HOW'D THEY KNOW YOU WERE AFK?
<P>DUDE. THE ZEK SERVER IS A DIFFERENT ANIMAL. BASICALLY YOU HAVE TO PRETEND IT IS MORE REALISTIC THAN THE OTHER FRUITY SERVERS. BOTTOM LINE....WOULD YOU TAKE A NAP OUTSIDE OF BEFALLEN IF YOU WERE REALLY THERE? JUST BECAUSE IT'S A GAME YOU FIGURE ....I'LL GO MAKE A SANDWHICH....SHAME ON YOU DUDE....YOU GOTTA KEEP YOUR EYES OPEN OR YOU ARE DONE FOR. THATS THE NAME OF THE GAME.
<P>Gray
<BR><a href="http://personal.lig.bellsouth.net/lig/g/r/grayrage/dbmain.htm">DarkenBane Company</a>
<P>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
